    <item>
      <title>南非将在 30 天内提供积分制和游牧签证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/south-africa-to-roll-out-new-visa-system-for-nomad-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非计划在 30 天内推出积分制，为想要在该国居住并为其他地方的组织远程工作的人们发放工作签证和许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/south-africa-to-roll-out-new-visa-system-for-nomad-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 14:16:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲东部寻求北约对俄罗斯侵犯领空作出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/europe-s-east-seeks-nato-response-to-russia-airspace-violations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[九个东欧国家的国防部长敦促北约针对俄罗斯侵犯乌克兰邻国领空的事件制定“集体答案”。]]></description>
